{"tid":2350642,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"acer spin系機想問下咁既情況有冇得整？","createTime":"2021-01-02T13:09:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T19:30:09.000Z","uid":329315,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e86533b63bf0b6bf9bc556017699f789b1bf058a","tid":2350642,"uid":329315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:09:02.000Z","msg":"之前部acer spin 5跌過落地，跟住個藍牙怪怪地，因為spin係摺mon機系列，我發現未摺前藍牙功能正常，摺mon後出現連接不穩甚至斷開既情況，問過一間電腦鋪話要拆mon整，但一般坊間鋪頭未必夠技術開mon驚整爆，叫我問acer原廠整。但我部機係大陸買，冇香港保養，acer話要整國際保養，但要單同當地身份證<strong><span class=\"red\">(大陸身份證)</span></strong>，唔明係咩邏輯，同埋我都冇<br />\n偏偏我要靠部機摺接連藍牙返工揾食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家變左連唔連到睇運數，可以點搞？"},{"pid":"8235ed14050b7be8b6f0fd0145941ab9ff755a89","tid":2350642,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"香港人去支那買機? 抵死"},{"pid":"8e2e18c13445748411e28101be8f6c65999166e8","tid":2350642,"uid":329315,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"8235ed14050b7be8b6f0fd0145941ab9ff755a89","tid":2350642,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:10:52.000Z","msg":"香港人去支那買機? 抵死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T13:22:06.000Z","msg":"癈話可以唔回喎，有冇睇清楚標題？"},{"pid":"8181b4dd0774ff041eefef7b922e9e3984364662","tid":2350642,"uid":193834,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T19:30:09.000Z","msg":"如果淨係藍牙出事，可以自己拆開背板，睇下藍牙卡有無鬆咗，整返實啲線試下先<br />\n張卡好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUVVuch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUVVuch.png&h=83693aed&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}